## How this file is maintained

`init` adds a row per experiment (⬜ designed). `conduct_exp <E>` flips it 🟦 while running,
✅ when all cells have data (❌ on failure). `process_outputs` sets 📊 once the experiment's
figures/tables and finding are rendered into the datestamped `.docx`.
